{
  "stem": "7458.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The hiding place we built above the tannery on the second story-- the whole second story was a triangle.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father had built a drying room for drying leather on that second story, so that-- so that there was a crawlspace above it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The crawlspace was about 20 feet wide, and about-- at the highest point, about 3 and 1/2, 4 feet high.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the building was a very long building, so that we constructed a little opening [POINTS] at the other end, at the back end of the tannery, where a ladder-- a rope ladder-- could be dropped.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You climbed up on a rope ladder until you were in the crawlspace.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then you crawled on your hands and knees about 80 or 90 feet to the front of the tannery, facing towards the street, where we had built a blind wall with boards that lifted out-- a whole little gate that lifted out-- where you could crawl in, put that little gate back into place, and that would create a wall just like the original wall, so that even if somebody came looking for us and crawled in that crawlspace, they would come to a wall that they thought was the end of the tannery, not knowing that behind that wall was about a 15- or 20-foot extra space where human beings were holding their breath, hiding.",
      "word_count": 116
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were also cracks in those boards so that we could see what's going on on the street.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And as many of us as could ran to that hiding place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We did not have time to dress, so we grabbed whatever we could, blankets, sheets, quilts, and a little bit of food.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we ran into that hiding place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'd say probably about 16, 17 people.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
